.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-4::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: 7up, cola, milk, coffee, soy-milk, mirinda, almond-milk
There are 7 different nationalities: japanese, american, french, turkish, colombian, spanish, russian
 1. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left of the french##1
 2. the person drinking soy-milk is on the right of the colombian##1
 3. the spanish is on the right of the turkish##1
 4. the person drinking soy-milk is on the right of the colombian##1
 5. the japanese is on the right of the person drinking 7up##1
 6. the turkish is between the person drinking milk and the spanish##2
 7. the person drinking 7up is in the middle##1
 8. the turkish is on the left of the person drinking coffee##1
 9. the person drinking cola is the american##1
10. the japanese is the person drinking almond-milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |     3     |   4    |     5      |     6     |    7     |
| Beverage      | milk    | soy-milk  | coffee  | 7up  | almond-milk      | mirinda       | cola |
| Nationality   | colombian | turkish | spanish | russian | japanese | french | american  |

