.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-5::.
The people prefer 7 different music-genres: pop, gospel, soul, salsa, d&b, blues, jazz
The people use 7 different means of transport: trike, boat, tram, subway, bus, quad-bike, car
1. the person driving the subway is on the right of the person driving the bus##1
2. the person driving the bus is the fan of gospel##1
3. the person driving the trike is between the fan of jazz and the fan of pop##2
4. the fan of blues is on the right of the person driving the bus##1
5. the person driving the trike is in the middle##1
6. the person driving the quad-bike is on the left of the fan of pop##1
7. the person driving the tram is on the left of the person driving the bus##1
8. the person driving the boat is the fan of salsa##1
9. the fan of d&b is the person driving the quad-bike##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2   |     3     |  4   |     5     |     6      |  7   |
| Music-Genre   | salsa      | d&b | pop | soul | jazz      | gospel      | blues |
| Transport     | boat | quad-bike | car       | trike | tram | bus | subway |

