.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-6::.
The people have 7 different jobs:  mechanic, doctor, librarian, dressmaker, architect, chef, teacher
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: handball, skiing, cricket, basketball, water-polo, soccer, golf
1. the librarian is on the left of the teacher##1
2. the person who's sport is cricket is the architect##1
3. the person who's sport is handball is on the left of the person who's sport is soccer##1
4. the doctor is on the left of the person who's sport is handball##1
5. the chef is on the right of the person who's sport is golf##1
6. the person who's sport is golf is between the person who's sport is water-polo and the mechanic##2
7. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the left of the person who's sport is skiing##1
8. the chef is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |      2      |        3        |      4       |     5     |     6     |   7    |
| Job     | architect | mechanic | dressmaker | chef | doctor | librarian     | teacher |
| Sport   | cricket   | basketball    | golf    | water-polo      | skiing  | handball | soccer |

