.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-7::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: water, soy-milk, 7up, tea, sprite, almond-milk, mirinda
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: golf, baseball, soccer, skateboarding, lacrosse, snowboarding, weightlifting
 1. the person who's sport is snowboarding is the person drinking sprite##1
 2. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
 3. the person who's sport is baseball is in the middle##1
 4. the person drinking 7up is between the person who's sport is lacrosse and the person who's sport is weightlifting##2
 5. the person who's sport is golf is on the left of the person drinking tea##1
 6. the person drinking water is on the left of the person who's sport is golf##1
 7. the person who's sport is skateboarding is the person drinking water##1
 8. the person drinking almond-milk is the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
 9. the person who's sport is soccer is between the person who's sport is lacrosse and the person drinking sprite##2
10. the person drinking 7up is on the left of the person drinking almond-milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |    2    |       3       |    4    |    5     |    6    |    7     |
| Beverage   | water | soy-milk    | tea | 7up   | almond-milk | mirinda    | sprite |
| Sport      | skateboarding | golf | weightlifting    | baseball | lacrosse    | soccer | snowboarding  |

