.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-8::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, milk, 7up, soy-milk, iced-tea, coffee, tea
The people have 7 different jobs:  bartender, chef, doctor, designer, scientist, architect, nurse
 1. the scientist is on the left of the designer##1
 2. the bartender is on the left of the doctor##1
 3. the architect is on the far left##1
 4. the person drinking milk is on the left of the person drinking tea##1
 5. the scientist is on the left of the person drinking milk##1
 6. the person drinking coffee is between the person drinking soy-milk and the person drinking tea##2
 7. the chef is on the right of the architect##1
 8. the bartender is on the right of the person drinking tea##1
 9. the person drinking milk is on the right of the person drinking almond-milk##1
10. the person drinking milk is between the person drinking tea and the person drinking almond-milk##2
11. the scientist is on the right of the person drinking iced-tea##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1        |     2      |      3       |     4     |         5          |     6      |     7     |
| Beverage   | 7up  | iced-tea   | almond-milk         | milk     | tea              | coffee    | soy-milk     |
| Job        | architect | chef | scientist | designer | nurse | bartender | doctor |

