.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-9::.
The people perfer 7 different movie-genres: crime, sports, documentary, spy, musical, zombie, fantasy
The people use 7 different means of transport: scooter, train, boat, bike, jet-ski, van, snowmobile
1. the person watching crime movies is the person driving the van##1
2. the person driving the train is on the left of the person watching crime movies##1
3. the person watching musical movies is between the person driving the snowmobile and the person driving the jet-ski##2
4. the person watching sports movies is on the left of the person watching spy movies##1
5. the person driving the scooter is in the middle##1
6. the person watching musical movies is on the left of the person watching documentary movies##1
7. the person driving the bike is on the left of the person driving the jet-ski##1
8. the person watching musical movies is on the right of the person watching zombie movies##1
9. the person driving the snowmobile is on the right of the person watching musical movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |   3    |    4    |    5     |     6     |   7    |
| Movie-Genre   | sports | spy     | zombie | musical | documentary | fantasy  | crime |
| Transport     | boat | bike | jet-ski   | scooter     | snowmobile    | train | van   |

