.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-10::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, almond-milk, lemonade, water, hot-chocolate, sprite, iced-tea
The people have 7 different hobbies: collecting, reading, chess, camping, drawing, skydiving, dancing
1. the person who's hobby is skydiving is the person drinking lemonade##1
2. the person drinking soy-milk is on the right of the person drinking almond-milk##1
3. the person who's hobby is chess is on the right of the person drinking almond-milk##1
4. the person who's hobby is skydiving is between the person who's hobby is camping and the person who's hobby is reading##2
5. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the left of the person who's hobby is chess##1
6. the person who's hobby is camping is on the far right##1
7. the person drinking iced-tea is on the right of the person drinking soy-milk##1
8. the person drinking water is between the person drinking hot-chocolate and the person who's hobby is skydiving##2
9. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the right of the person who's hobby is collecting##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |     2     |      3      |      4       |    5    |      6      |    7    |
| Beverage   | almond-milk  | soy-milk       | iced-tea         | hot-chocolate         | water   | lemonade        | sprite |
| Hobby      | dancing | chess | collecting | drawing | reading | skydiving | camping  |

