.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-11::.
The people have 7 different hobbies: traveling, camping, fishing, photography, gardening, magic-tricks, baking
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: parkour, rowing, badminton, cricket, snowboarding, cycling, skiing
1. the person who's sport is skiing is on the far right##1
2. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the right of the person who's sport is rowing##1
3. the person who's hobby is gardening is in the middle##1
4. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the right of the person who's sport is parkour##1
5. the person who's sport is parkour is on the right of the person who's sport is badminton##1
6. the person who's hobby is photography is between the person who's sport is snowboarding and the person who's hobby is camping##2
7. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is between the person who's hobby is fishing and the person who's hobby is baking##2
8. the person who's hobby is baking is on the left of the person who's sport is cricket##1
9. the person who's hobby is camping is on the left of the person who's hobby is traveling##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |       2       |     3      |       4       |    5    |     6      |       7       |
| Hobby   | baking | magic-tricks       | fishing    | gardening | photography | camping     | traveling       |
| Sport   | rowing    | cricket | cycling | snowboarding        | badminton | parkour | skiing |

