.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-12::.
The people perfer 7 different movie-genres: disaster, animation, satire, sports, martial-arts, mystery, scientific
The people prefer 7 different music-genres: hip-hop, gospel, trance, techno, jazz, funk, d&b
 1. the person watching disaster movies is the fan of d&b##1
 2. the person watching scientific movies is on the left of the fan of jazz##1
 3. the person watching disaster movies is between the person watching sports movies and the fan of hip-hop##2
 4. the person watching mystery movies is between the person watching scientific movies and the person watching martial-arts movies##2
 5. the fan of funk is on the right of the fan of trance##1
 6. the fan of trance is on the right of the fan of hip-hop##1
 7. the person watching satire movies is on the far right##1
 8. the person watching satire movies is the fan of jazz##1
 9. the fan of techno is on the far left##1
10. the fan of techno is the person watching sports movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |   3   |   4   |    5    |   6    |   7    |
| Movie-Genre   | sports | disaster | animation  | martial-arts   | mystery | scientific | satire |
| Music-Genre   | techno     | d&b       | hip-hop | trance | funk  | gospel   | jazz   |

