 5. the fan of techno is on the left of the fan of punk##1
 6. the person drinking lemonade is on the right of the fan of gospel##1
 7. the fan of techno is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1
 8. the fan of r&b is on the right of the person drinking juice##1
 9. the fan of dubstep is on the left of the person drinking water##1
10. the person drinking water is on the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1

