 4. the person drinking avocadoade is on the far left##1
 5. the person eating potato is on the left of the person eating kale##1
 6. the person eating plum is the person drinking coffee##1
 7. the person drinking sprite is the person eating kale##1
 8. the person eating cranberry is on the right of the person eating kale##1
 9. the person drinking soy-milk is between the person drinking 7up and the person eating plum##2
