.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-15::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: coffee, cola, almond-milk, tea, sprite, 7up, juice
There 7 different types of food: cherry, pumpkin, artichoke, apple, cucumber, cranberry, lemon
 1. the person drinking juice is on the right of the person eating lemon##1
 2. the person drinking cola is in the middle##1
 3. the person eating cucumber is on the right of the person drinking 7up##1
 4. the person drinking almond-milk is between the person drinking juice and the person eating cherry##2
 5. the person eating apple is the person drinking almond-milk##1
 6. the person drinking coffee is on the left of the person drinking 7up##1
 7. the person eating lemon is the person drinking cola##1
 8. the person eating artichoke is the person eating artichoke##1
 9. the person drinking cola is on the left of the person eating pumpkin##1
10. the person eating artichoke is on the left of the person drinking sprite##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |    2    |     3     |       4       |      5      |    6     |    7     |
| Beverage   | coffee       | 7up | sprite      | cola | juice       | almond-milk | tea |
| Food       | cranberry | artichoke    | cucumber | lemon    | pumpkin | apple   | cherry |

