3. the person who's hobby is reading is on the left of the person who's sport is skateboarding##1
4. the person who's hobby is reading is between the person who's hobby is camping and the person who's sport is skateboarding##2
5. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the right of the person who's hobby is reading##1
6. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the left of the person who's sport is skiing##1
7. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the left of the person who's hobby is camping##1
8. the person who's sport is skiing is on the left of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
9. the person who's sport is tennis is on the right of the person who's sport is cycling##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |       2       |     3     |     4     |      5      |    6     |    7     |
